WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.500
Alice Smith: Good morning everyone. Today we are reviewing the Q2 contract renewals with our top clients.

2
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:18.200
Bob Johnson: Thanks Alice. I have reviewed the Contoso agreement and there are three clauses that need legal sign-off before we proceed.

3
00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:30.500
Alice Smith: Agreed. The liability cap in section 4.2 is particularly important. Legal has flagged it as a potential risk given the new data protection regulations.

4
00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:42.000
Carol Lee: From the customer service side, clients have been asking about the SLA terms in appendix B. We need to clarify the response time commitments.

5
00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:55.500
Bob Johnson: I will schedule a follow-up with the legal team this week. We should have a draft ready by Friday.
